---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const lastUpdated = new Date().toLocaleDateString();
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - WorkFlowAI" description="Read our Privacy Policy to understand how we collect, use, and protect your data.">
  <div class="relative overflow-hidden pt-12 pb-24">
    <!-- Glowing background effects -->
    <div class="glow-orb glow-orb-indigo" style="top:-10%;left:-10%"></div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
      <div class="border-b border-white/6 pb-8 mb-10">
        <h1 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Last Updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-panel p-8 rounded-3xl border border-white/6 space-y-6 text-gray-300">
        <p class="leading-relaxed">At WorkFlowAI, we take your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy describes how your personal information is collected, used, and shared when you visit or interact with our site.</p>
        
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8">1. Information We Collect</h3>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">When you visit the Site, we automatically collect certain information about your device, including information about your web browser, IP address, time zone, and some of the cookies that are installed on your device.</p>
        
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8">2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">We use the collected information to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Deliver downloadable assets and blueprint files;</li>
          <li>Communicate with you via our newsletter (if subscribed);</li>
          <li>Screen site transactions for potential risk or fraud; and</li>
          <li>Analyze how visitors navigate and utilize our platform to improve overall user experience.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8">3. Sharing Your Personal Information</h3>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">We share your Personal Information with third parties to help us analyze site performance, as described above. For example, we use Google Analytics to help us understand how our customers use the Site.</p>
        
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8">4. Your Rights</h3>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">You have the right to access personal information we hold about you and to ask that your personal information be corrected, updated, or deleted. If you would like to exercise this right, please contact us.</p>
        
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8">5. Contact Us</h3>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">For more information about our privacy practices, if you have questions, or if you would like to make a complaint, please contact us by e-mail at <a href="mailto:hello@workflowai.site" class="text-indigo-400 hover:underline">hello@workflowai.site</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
